HEADWORD: Superficialist
<hw>Su`per*fi"cial*ist</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who attends to
anything superficially; a superficial or shallow person; a sciolist; a
smatterer.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

